{"id": "1483119812665147554", "channel_id": "1462840887553032335", "type": 0, "author_id": "1340549333359132753", "author_name": "150_ripe", "author_bot": false, "content": "我认了，明天省一测，考前发疯已经是常态了当你们一边闲聊，一边离开此地时<:Aurita_pinch:1468258028271833119> \n\n一山离愁，\n无声隐匿在雾中。\n灯火微弱，\n难辨你远去行踪。\n故垒依旧只是人去楼空，\n柔绡轻轻走过空留潮起潮落。\n\n一路繁忧，\n行至天涯忘回首。\n独守林中，\n新醅枉阻人漂泊。\n月不停留团圆更难求，\n长夜后东方仍未现那抹红。\n\n表达了作者的思乡之情<:Aurita_pinch:1468258028271833119>", "timestamp": "2026-03-16T15:08:38.373000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🛐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1483119811952251030", "filename": "IMG_20260316_225404.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 341936}, {"id": "1483119812380196864", "filename": "IMG_20260316_225424.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 507500}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
